00:24:57,042 --> 00:25:00,792
POMPÉIA, ITÁLIA

402
00:25:08,208 --> 00:25:11,418
79 DC

403
00:25:12,667 --> 00:25:15,247
-Aqui vamos nós.
-A qualquer minuto agora.

404
00:25:15,333 --> 00:25:18,133
